  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>There are two houses in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> named Fossoway:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/20px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/30px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/40px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway of Cider Hall</a> (oft called the red-apple Fossoways)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/20px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/30px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/40px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">House Fossoway of New Barrel</a> (oft called the green-apple Fossoways)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403133733\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.042 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 17/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 83/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 332/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua v